Use Case: View Reviewing Assignment				PRIORITY:  HIGH	Use Case #:  R-5
Actor: Reviewer
Preconditions
1.	User is logged in and viewing Reviewer Home page
2.	List of reviewing assignments shown as a result of being on Reviewer Home page
Normal Course
1.	User selects assignment to view
2.	User downloads submitted pdf 
3.	Add message to log file
Alternative Course (ERROR)
2.	Error in downloading file should be reported to user (on screen) with appropriate details
3.	(ERROR) message added to log
4.	User is given option to return to list of reviewing assignments (Step #1 of normal course)
Post conditions
1.	User will have downloaded file (if no error)
2.	User will remain on Reviewing Assignment page


